---
// PreviewBanner.astro
---

<div class="preview-banner banner" role="status">
  <span class="preview-banner__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
  <p class="preview-banner__text">
    This is a <strong>preview</strong> site intended for prototyping and not for
    production use. Some content was generated by Copilot (AI) and is purely meant
    for demo purposes.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .preview-banner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-inline: var(--layout-gap-inline, 2rem);
    background: #fffbe6;
    color: #856404;
    padding-block: 0.75rem;
    border-block-end: 1px solid var(--color-border, #ddd);
  }
  .preview-banner__icon {
    font-size: 1.25em;
  }

  .preview-banner__text {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
